{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f6f1fcd73e","title":"对学校领导骨干、教材等问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fedb106ba9","index":0,"year":1953,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wansui3","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949-1957卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui3a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"387733ceec","type":"title","text":"对学校领导骨干、教材等问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"54c2499316","type":"paragraph","text":"1.领导骨干：大专院校，中学必须有骨干。骨干配备大专由中央组织部负责，中学由地方负责，从宣传部门，青年团干部下去。有了好校长就有好教师。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c1a3105082","type":"paragraph","text":"2.教材问题：集中力量编，语文、历史等原则问题，由陈伯达同志等解决。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1b3875b5fa","type":"paragraph","text":"3.整顿小学：防止过“左”，教育发展的不平衡性，要照顾农村特点。私也要让其存在。小学有三类：（1）中心小学、完全小学：（2）一般小学；（3）速成小学。小学问题主要便利农民子弟入学。教师只要不是现行犯，不作反革命宣传就可存在。对超龄学生不应赶出，首先教好。民办可办，不要求太严，群众需要自愿，学费可收。五年一贯制暂缓执行，提早了。小学生不能都升学，这不叫失学，要加强劳动教育。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f69dccf3d5","type":"paragraph","text":"4.学生健康，高中大部分要有助学金，要增加营养，减轻负担。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"06314874a1","type":"paragraph","text":"5.教育工作重点和关键：重点是高等学校和高中，关键问题是师资。中学要重点办好一批。如何办好高中，这是我们的重点任务。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b58b3a75a7","type":"paragraph","text":"6.招生要注意成分。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d8e2cd7887","type":"paragraph","text":"7.速成识字法，在农村有局限性。应是群众自愿的业务教育。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"101f026181","type":"paragraph","text":"8.中央教育部任务：（1）方针计划；（2）教材。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"85c944cf51","type":"paragraph","text":"9.总的方针和工作重点：过去主要毛病是盲目冒进，不能适应建设，我们任务是培养干部和逐渐适应生产发展，目前在培养","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"84db073a1c","type":"subtitle","text":"干部。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":493,"end":492}},"wansui3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"361f2d3fcf","type":"paragraph","text":"6、招生要注意成分。","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3ce3157b5e","type":"paragraph","text":"4、学生建康，高中大部分要有助学金，要增加营养，减轻负担。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"702d9cc245","type":"paragraph","text":"9、总的方针和工作重点：过去主要毛病是盲目冒进，不能适应建设，我们任务是培养干部和逐渐（适应）生产发展，目前在培养干部。","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"911af610eb","type":"title","text":"对学校领导骨干、教材等问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c98ad6cd6a","type":"paragraph","text":"l、领导骨干：大专院校，中学必须有骨干。骨干配备大专由中央组织部负责，中学由地方负责，从宣传部门，青年团干部下去。有了好校长就有好教师。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cb1266d52f","type":"paragraph","text":"7、速成识字法，在农村有局限性。应是群众自愿的业务教育。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ed50ac8108","type":"paragraph","text":"2、教材问题：集中力量编，语文、历史等原则问题，由陈伯达同志等解决。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fa05870368","type":"paragraph","text":"8、中央教育部任务：（1）方针计划；（2）教材。","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fa05bac39e","type":"paragraph","text":"3、整顿小学：防止过左，教育发展的不平衡性，要照顾农村特点。私塾也要让其存在。小学有三类：（1）中心小学、完全小学；（2）一般小学；（3）速成小学。小学问题主要便利农民子弟入学。教师只要不是现行犯，不做反革命宣传就可存在。对超龄学生不应赶出，首先教好。民办可办，不要求太严，群众需要自愿，学费可收。五年一贯制暂缓执行，提早了。小学生不能都升学，这不叫失学，要加强劳动教育。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ffdc73b6c6","type":"paragraph","text":"5、教育工作重点和关键：重点，高等学校和高中，关键问题是师资。中学要重点办好一批。如何办好高中，这是我们的重点任务。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"f6f1fcd73e","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":90,"end":89}}}},"__N_SSG":true}